260
00:15:28,420 --> 00:15:29,520
Apa?

261
00:15:31,020 --> 00:15:32,460
Bukankah itu Saet...

262
00:15:32,689 --> 00:15:34,819
Dal Sik, ayahmu sedang bicara!

263
00:15:36,830 --> 00:15:38,330
Ada pepatah, "Jika tak bagus,
itu bukanlah akhir."

264
00:15:38,400 --> 00:15:40,570
Geum Bi, kau sangat hebat.

265
