268
00:15:51,740 --> 00:15:52,980
Di sana.

269
00:15:54,280 --> 00:15:55,510
- Merunduk!
- Merunduk.

270
00:15:56,920 --> 00:15:59,550
- Kau sungguh melihat Saet Byul?
- Ya, aku melihatnya.

271
00:15:59,620 --> 00:16:01,650
Aku punya mata elang.

272
00:16:01,675 --> 00:16:02,745
Di mana?

273
00:16:03,720 --> 00:16:05,120
Aku harus ke mana?

274
00:16:08,990 --> 00:16:11,060
Geum Bi, kau di mana?

275
00:16:11,130 --> 00:16:12,430
Aku di sini.

276
00:16:13,337 --> 00:16:14,707
Aku terkejut.

277
00:16:15,002 --> 00:16:17,972
Aku tak bisa membedakan antara kau
dan bunga, bahkan dengan mata elangku.

278
00:16:18,100 --> 00:16:20,710
- Aw, kau!
- Jangan menakutiku.

279
00:16:21,640 --> 00:16:23,010
Ayolah.

280
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:25,180
Geum Bi.

281
00:16:30,427 --> 00:16:31,487
Ottokㅡv

