- Benarkah?

288
00:16:48,870 --> 00:16:50,369
Tanah kami dimulai...

289
00:16:50,440 --> 00:16:51,899
Aku mengerti. Cepat hubungi dia.

290
00:16:54,139 --> 00:16:56,010
Kenapa dia ada di Onyang?

291
00:16:56,580 --> 00:16:57,980
Aku tak bisa memahami dia.

292
00:17:00,280 --> 00:17:03,520
Dae Hyun, jangan terkejut
dan dengarkan saja aku.

293
00:17:03,750 --> 00:17:06,919
Saet Byul bekerja di kebun keluargaku.

294
00:17:07,820 --> 00:17:09,990
Kirimkan alamatnya. Terima kasih.

295
00:17:12,860 --> 00:17:14,230
"Anda harus membayar parkir."

296
00:17:14,990 --> 00:17:17,500
"Jumlah 6000 won"
"Bayar"

297
00:17:31,140 --> 00:17:33,280
Tebak siapa ini! Kami kembali!

298
00:17:35,910 --> 00:17:37,350
Pada kemana? Kok sepi?

299
00:17:38,820 --> 00:17:40,090
Siapa kalian?

300
00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:44,320
- Siapa kau?
- Apa kau pencuri?

301
00:17:44,351 --> 00:17:47,830
Baru beberapa hari aku meninggalkan
Shinseong-dong, dan sekarang ada pencuri?

302
00:17:50,560 --> 00:17:52,900
