- Bagaimana perjalanan kalian?

303
00:17:52,970 --> 00:17:55,600
Kemarilah! Ada pencuri.

304
00:17:55,625 --> 00:17:58,455
Waduh. Kau baik-baik saja?

305
00:17:58,570 --> 00:18:00,440
Dia pemilik toko yang baru!

306
00:18:00,510 --> 00:18:01,610
- Pemilik baru?
- Ya.

307
00:18:01,670 --> 00:18:04,280
- Bangunkan dia kembali!
- Aku tak tahu caranya!

308
00:18:04,340 --> 00:18:05,880
- Ayo!
- Aku tahu.

309
00:18:09,480 --> 00:18:10,980
Dia sadar.

310
00:18:11,850 --> 00:18:14,190
Kau menjual toserbamu?

311
00:18:14,550 --> 00:18:17,035
Bukan begitu, karena kini Dae Hyun
bekerja di kantor pusat,

312
00:18:17,060 --> 00:18:18,360
kantor pusat mengelola toko ini.

313
00:18:18,385 --> 00:18:20,555
Ayo ngerumpi di luar.

314
00:18:20,660 --> 00:18:21,930
Sampai jumpa.

315
00:18:22,290 --> 00:18:24,100
- Maafkan aku.
- Tentu.

316
00:18:24,900 --> 00:18:26,060
Aigoo.

317
00:18:27,827 --> 00:18:29,427
Kalian bersenang-senang?

318
00:18:30,740 --> 00:18:32,700
Zhangjiajie luar biasa.

319
00:18:32,770 --> 00:18:36,110
Dan kami memberi tahu Jang Mi
tentang keadaanmu.

320
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:40,480
Benarkah?

321
00:18:42,439 --> 00:18:43,579
Aigoo, dasar...

322
00:18:43,616 --> 00:18:46,186
Kami punya hadiah untukmu.

323
00:18:46,350 --> 00:18:47,450
Apa ini?

324
00:18:49,350 --> 00:18:50,990
Ini luar biasa!

325
00:18:53,860 --> 00:18:55,430
Itu membuatmu ingin seperti ini.

326
00:19:26,890 --> 00:19:27,960
Jomjang-nim?

327
00:19:29,430 --> 00:19:30,830
Bagaimana kau bisa kemari?

328
00:19:30,900 --> 00:19:32,200
Apa maksudmu?

329
00:19:33,270 --> 00:19:35,870
Kau pernah menemukanku.
Kenapa aku tak bisa menemukanmu?

330
00:19:37,100 --> 00:19:40,340
Hei, Jung Saet Byul.
Kenapa kau membohongiku?

331
00:19:40,940 --> 00:19:44,410
Ini bukan akhir hubungan kita.

332
00:19:45,310 --> 00:19:46,780
Ini adalah awalnya.

333
00:19:52,890 --> 00:19:54,750
Semua sudah berakhir.

334
00:19:55,350 --> 00:19:56,520
Aku sibuk.

335
00:19:59,020 --> 00:19:59,790
Saet Byul...

336
00:19:59,860 --> 00:20:02,590
Aneh sekali, kenapa hujan?

337
00:20:04,660 --> 00:20:08,100
Apa itu kau? Yang mematahkan lengan adikku?

338
00:20:08,670 --> 00:20:11,840
Bukan, wanita yang di sebelah sana.

339
00:20:12,300 --> 00:20:15,510
Apa? Kau dipukuli perempuan?

340
00:20:15,910 --> 00:20:19,140
Dasar bodoh! Memalukan sekali.

341
00:20:19,210 --> 00:20:20,180
Dasar sialan.

342
00:20:20,980 --> 00:20:23,980
Saet Byul, apa yang terjadi?
Apa terjadi sesuatu?

343
00:20:24,250 --> 00:20:25,280
Tidak.

344
00:20:26,550 --> 00:20:30,090
Aku hanya membantu seseorang.

345
00:20:32,290 --> 00:20:33,290
Permisi,

346
00:20:33,819 --> 00:20:36,206
kami sedang membicarakan
hal yang sangat penting.

347
00:20:36,530 --> 00:20:40,530
Kurasa kalian tak bisa
bicara baik-baik dengan kami.

348
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:42,270
Bisa pergi saja?

349
00:20:42,470 --> 00:20:45,770
Apa aku mendengar gonggongan anjing Seoul?

350
00:20:47,110 --> 00:20:49,370
Kalian berdua bisa bicara sesuka kalian...

351
00:20:49,440 --> 00:20:50,910
...saat kalian mati.

352
00:20:52,689 --> 00:20:54,089
Saet Byul, pilih.

353
00:20:54,650 --> 00:20:57,220
- Apa?
- Jika kau memilih satu,

354
00:20:57,280 --> 00:20:59,420
kau akan melihat sisi baru diriku.

355
00:20:59,850 --> 00:21:01,490
Jika kau memilih dua,

356
00:21:02,020 --> 00:21:04,020
kau akan melihat pria yang kau kenal.

357
00:21:04,090 --> 00:21:05,260
Pilihlah.

358
00:21:06,890 --> 00:21:07,960
Aku...

359
00:21:08,330 --> 00:21:09,830
Jangan khawatir. Pilih saja.

360
00:21:13,870 --> 00:21:15,000
Jomjang-nim,

361
00:21:17,540 --> 00:21:18,640
nomor satu.

362
00:21:23,340 --> 00:21:24,500
Pilihan yang bagus.

363
00:21:34,690 --> 00:21:36,790
Tumitnya menyentuh lantai,

364
00:21:36,860 --> 00:21:38,120
artinya dia tak lincah.

365
00:21:40,211 --> 00:21:41,981
Itu pose khas orang-orang
bertangan kanan.

366
00:21:42,530 --> 00:21:44,730
Dia lebih sering memukul jab daripada hook.

367
00:21:45,830 --> 00:21:49,000
Ini artinya dia hanyalah preman jalanan.

368
00:21:50,740 --> 00:21:52,370
Jika dia maju dengan 1, 2, dan tinjuan,

369
00:21:55,870 --> 00:21:58,840
kalau begitu, aku akan membalasnya.

370
00:22:00,780 --> 00:22:02,580
Jomjang-nim! Dia keren sekali.

371
00:22:08,250 --> 00:22:10,290
Dia menyerangku dengan 1, 2, dan tinjuan.

372
00:22:10,690 --> 00:22:11,820
Kalau begitu, aku akan...

373
00:22:18,072 --> 00:22:19,682
- Jomjang-nim!
- Apa itu tadi?

374
00:22:20,370 --> 00:22:21,970
Jomjang-nim?

375
00:22:22,270 --> 00:22:23,840
Omo, Jomjang-nim,
kau baik-baik saja?

376
00:22:23,900 --> 00:22:26,000
- Jomjang-nim!
- Sudah selesai?

377
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:28,610
Ini kali pertama aku bertemu
pengecut seperti ini.

378
00:22:28,670 --> 00:22:30,880
Kalian lihat itu?
Aku sedikit takut tadi.

379
00:22:32,380 --> 00:22:34,450
Sial. Beraninya kau menyakiti Jomjang-nim?

380
00:22:35,080 --> 00:22:37,780
Jomjang-nim, tunggu. Ya?

381
00:22:37,850 --> 00:22:39,150
Bernapaslah!

382
00:22:47,860 --> 00:22:49,830
Aku bos di sini. Habisi dia.

383
00:22:50,500 --> 00:22:51,530
Lawan aku.

384
00:23:03,059 --> 00:23:04,959
Apa-apaan itu?

385
00:23:06,750 --> 00:23:07,810
Beraninya kau.

386
00:23:11,920 --> 00:23:13,520
Jangan berani menggangguku lagi.

387
00:23:14,120 --> 00:23:16,350
Baik! Lepaskan aku.

388
00:23:17,960 --> 00:23:20,430
- Jomjang-nim!
- Astaga.

389
00:23:20,490 --> 00:23:21,760
Tunggu apa? Cepat keluar!

390
00:23:22,260 --> 00:23:23,430
Cepat!

391
00:23:23,500 --> 00:23:24,900
Jomjang-nim, kau baik-baik saja?

392
00:23:25,160 --> 00:23:27,200
Mereka semua sudah pergi. Bangun.

393
00:23:27,270 --> 00:23:28,300
Jomjang-nim?

394
00:23:28,600 --> 00:23:31,140
Hei!

395
00:23:31,600 --> 00:23:33,340
Mereka semua pergi ke mana?

396
00:23:33,410 --> 00:23:35,540
Di mana mereka?

397
00:23:35,840 --> 00:23:37,940
Mereka semua kabur karena takut padamu.

398
00:23:37,965 --> 00:23:40,435
Apa? Aku menakuti mereka?

399
00:23:42,071 --> 00:23:43,027
Anak-anak itu...

400
00:23:43,052 --> 00:23:45,495
