00:25:48,730 --> 00:25:49,737
Aku pamit.

433
00:25:59,980 --> 00:26:02,580
!0 tahun lalu, taekwondo,
memukul Sandbag, Jung Saet Byul.

434
00:26:07,397 --> 00:26:08,957
Saat itu kau berterima kasih, 'kan?

435
00:26:11,900 --> 00:26:13,730
Aku senang mendengarnya.

436
00:26:14,451 --> 00:26:16,500
Setelah dengar itu,
aku mulai membantu orang lain.

437
00:26:21,702 --> 00:26:24,702
Jadi, terima kasih, Saet Byul.

438
00:26:26,810 --> 00:26:27,950
Aku akan menunggumu.

439
00:26:29,810 --> 00:26:30,920
Selain itu...

440
00:26:36,350 --> 00:26:38,120
Aku ingin mengatakan sesuatu.

441
00:26:39,460 --> 00:26:40,490
Saet Byul,

442
00:26:44,160 --> 00:26:45,600
